param.description:
scheme to allocate land runoff:
                        0 - precip. (default);
                        1 - bucket overflow
                        2 - Leaky bucket (Meissner et al '03);
                        3 - soil moisture 'half-life'

if ea_par_runoff_scheme=2,
                        this determines the Clapp-Hornberger exponent
                        (4.50 for coarse grain soil; 6.63 for medium and 11.20 for fine grain)
